      "text": "（「五限目です。寂しいからってこころにダル絡み）\n（せず、莉央さんもロケ頑張って下さい」っと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（'It's the fifth period. Don't get involved with Kokoro just because you're lonely）\n（Rio-san‚ do your best on location'）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3000004401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
